-Xu%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-Bard1OcbywhseuNdN-aKzQ">Tứ thời thi - Xuân từ - 四時詩－春詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Chi-Lan/author-I8hgXoJ_4jxqBTTiU5WM8g">Ngô Chi Lan</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Dung/%E1%BB%A8c-s%C6%A1n-tuy%E1%BB%81n/poem-bdDx4PX3Z8fg38HkcDCcOw">Ức sơn tuyền - 憶山泉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Dung/author-qoi_3MEdeZkoj0TClsekFA">Ngô Dung</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1n-H%C6%B0u/V%C3%A3n-b%E1%BA%A1c-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-giang-t%C3%A1c/poem-3BZWSGgESwZkGKWcuL_XzA">Vãn bạc Tương giang tác - 晚泊湘江作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1n-H%C6%B0u/author-SWshGEoAx645s4epx95yPA">Quán Hưu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem--_vtrN6QzVoY9q8h_0zqlg">Xuân nhật kỳ 3 - 春日其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br></div>	</div>
